item.title: Tech NEWS 2021-12-30
item.description: Future autonomous Waymo EV will be custom built for ride-hailing with no steering wheel (2 minute read) Waymo is collaborating with Geely, a Chinese automotive company, to create an EV for its US ride-hailing service.

item.title: Tech NEWS 2021-06-11
item.description: How to watch the debut of Tesla Model S Plaid, the ‘quickest production car ever made’ (4 minute read) Tesla revealed a new high-performance Plaid version of the Model S on Thursday on a livestream.

item.title: Tech NEWS 2021-06-04
item.description: Waymo’s driverless taxi service can now be accessed on Google Maps (2 minute read) Waymo One can now be accessed and booked through Google Maps.

item.title: Tech NEWS 2020-10-09
item.description: Waymo’s robo-taxi service opens to the public in Phoenix (3 minute read) Waymo is relaunching its fully automated robo-taxi ride-hailing service in Phoenix.
